@startuml
title Export/Import Keyring
autonumber

actor "Target device user" as TargetUser
participant "Target device" as Target
collections "Out-of-band transfer" as OOB
participant "Source device" as Source
actor "Source device user" as SourceUser

Target -> Target: Generate or load X25519 device keypair
Target --> TargetUser: Show device public key
TargetUser --> SourceUser: Send public key out-of-band
SourceUser -> Source: Select profile type and dialogues
Source -> Source: Build ExportPayload JSON
Source -> Source: Include selected keyrings and requested client/admin roles
Source -> Source: Generate ephemeral X25519 keypair
Source -> Source: ECDH(ephemeral private, target public)
Source -> Source: HKDF-SHA256 -> ChaCha20-Poly1305 key
Source -> Source: Encrypt payload into JSON envelope {v, eph_pub, nonce, ct}
Source --> OOB: Transfer export file without server involvement
OOB --> Target: Import encrypted export file
Target -> Target: ECDH(device private, eph_pub)
Target -> Target: HKDF-SHA256 -> ChaCha20-Poly1305 key
Target -> Target: Decrypt and validate payload version/profile type
Target -> Target: Merge by server + username + peer + start_seq
Target -> Target: Skip identical entries and reject conflicting keys
Target --> TargetUser: Show import counts and offer to delete export file

@enduml
